{"tid":1213603,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"今次我地要一個服務香港人嘅政府","createTime":"2019-06-13T02:08:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-13T03:18:03.000Z","uid":222328,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"7f18f73e045d178691c78c62c1a43b9f62930612","tid":1213603,"uid":222328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T02:08:56.000Z","msg":"撤回逃犯條例只不過係緩兵之計<br />\n一百萬人上街遊行，政府無動於衷。<br />\n如果我地再和理非非，政府撤回逃犯條例都只不過係因為基於國際壓力，而唔係因為要對市民負責。<br />\n撤回逃犯條例只係政府緩兵之計。03年有第廿三條，19年有逃犯條例，過多幾年又再推過另一條惡法，咁到時又要再衝多次？ 個時已經冇人會再衝，衝得嘅都已經俾人拉哂。<br />\n再講，就算政府會撤回方案都係因為外國嘅壓力。你估過左今次，外資仲敢唔敢留係香港？應該會好似李嘉誠咁慢慢撤資。今次，佢地唔夠時間撤資。下次呢？錢都已經走哂，佢地仲會唔會理哩個地方？下次再推嘅時候，我地只有硬食。<br />\n今日，可能最後一個機會有咁多香港人企出黎，我地要嘅唔單止係撤回逃犯條例，今次我地要一個服務香港人嘅政府，同香港人一齊對抗中央嘅政府。<br />\n衝得嘅話，今次唔可以再袋住先。"},{"pid":"b5309d4c3ed17c7b32c6781a3e008f61a5c79798","tid":1213603,"uid":222328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T02:09:06.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"70bc60a7694a0fc4f61bcf0ed002171ea7f9cd53","tid":1213603,"uid":222328,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T02:09:16.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"fffb910f2dce67efe0512720ef9932a30235ae85","tid":1213603,"uid":222328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T02:13:35.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"751f872406e047b6a59f360a5f68acd22aaf0a21","tid":1213603,"uid":222328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T02:13:52.000Z","msg":"Push俾多啲人見到"},{"pid":"d5e399301457f32b1b9ddcfe5cd3d8ddead7006d","tid":1213603,"uid":222328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T02:20:51.000Z","msg":"Push push"},{"pid":"041e597ad2fa6d8af8a496d69619bf4cc62b85f3","tid":1213603,"uid":222328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T02:21:01.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"89a7c804cc97f657dcbb6124078dee4c360c5303","tid":1213603,"uid":222328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T02:21:15.000Z","msg":"獨立係唯一出路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84b31249dba39afcc193001e1726be12ee5d00bb","tid":1213603,"uid":222328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T02:21:52.000Z","msg":"如果唔係遲早香港都會俾大陸玩殘"},{"pid":"2fae38f6b0b08d6ab730cd01d3921e15d880c122","tid":1213603,"uid":222328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T02:24:44.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"b5e01f5bafad00a6a6655767a3fddb2c847aaaa5","tid":1213603,"uid":222328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T02:25:02.000Z","msg":"港共政權<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fba01dacb77180fbb9dac193d60dd3baa323767","tid":1213603,"uid":222328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T02:28:52.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"cf2c028524fa7442390e686a2966ab8bc28dde90","tid":1213603,"uid":222328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T02:50:06.000Z","msg":"唔好再淨係為逃犯條例啦"},{"pid":"7a285f5ecdc8f72e05c55299a92748c69391b3f5","tid":1213603,"uid":222328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T03:18:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}